00:11:09.380 --> 00:11:17.680
So that and that was the very first stream of gas from a center of a galaxy ever observed by humanity in 1980.

00:11:18.020 --> 00:11:20.640
Didn't know that it was going to be a black hole at the time.

00:11:20.640 --> 00:11:27.280
